From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Sun, 1 Mar 2026 08:09:06 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 47/47] Issue 684: Add CreateDevToolsTab with synthetic URL
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

A new XPC command arrives in town,
"create_devtools_tab" — please sit down.
No GURL parsing tricks,
Just integers that fix,
The bug that once brought DevTools crashing down.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
